Docs.summary: Reads the next ZIP file entry and positions the stream at the beginning of the entry data.
Docs.value: the next ZIP file entry, or null if there are no more entries

remarks.para: Reads the next ZIP file entry and positions the stream at the beginning of the entry data.
If the app targets Android U or above, zip file entry names containing ".." or starting with "/" passed here will throw a ZipException. For more details, see dalvik.system.ZipPathValidator.
